In `src/app/api/expense-transactions/route.ts`, in the GET handler:
Remove the block that parses `tagIds` from searchParams and assigns `whereClause.tags`:
```
const tagIds = searchParams.get('tagIds');
if (tagIds) {
  const tagIdArray = tagIds.split(',').filter(Boolean);
  if (tagIdArray.length > 0) {
    whereClause.tags = {
      some: {
        id: { in: tagIdArray },
      },
    };
  }
}
```
Do NOT remove the `tagIds` field from the Zod schema or the POST handler.
Do NOT remove tag-name search in the `search` param handling.
